WEBVTT


00:01:22.519 --> 00:01:24.519
I like someone just like you.

00:01:24.519 --> 00:01:25.319
Let go.

00:01:30.519 --> 00:01:31.519
Who are you?

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:33.120
I've booked this place.

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:34.000
Get lost.

00:01:37.159 --> 00:01:38.040
Tie Tuo Wang.

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:39.159
Highly skilled in martial arts.

00:01:39.319 --> 00:01:41.159
Sent to Haicheng to support Gu Zhantian.

00:01:41.560 --> 00:01:43.920
Will become a capable general under Gu Zhantian in the future.

00:01:44.840 --> 00:01:46.319
This guy's combat power is very high.

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:47.599
I can't afford to mess with him.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:51.319
Well, since

00:01:51.319 --> 00:01:52.439
you've booked this place,

00:01:53.239 --> 00:01:54.040
I'll leave it to you.

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:54.959
Let's go.

00:01:56.959 --> 00:01:58.519
You can get lost by yourself.

00:01:58.959 --> 00:01:59.920
She stays.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:02.319
Looks like a fight is inevitable today.

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:03.519
Calm down.

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:05.159
There must be a way out of this.

00:02:05.959 --> 00:02:06.760
Right.

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:08.520
The character bio just said

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:10.960
Tie Tuo Wang was sent to support Gu Zhantian,

00:02:11.159 --> 00:02:13.120
and will only become his subordinate in the future.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:15.439
Which means there's a possibility

00:02:15.639 --> 00:02:16.280
that right now,

00:02:16.280 --> 00:02:17.639
he hasn't met Gu Zhantian yet.

00:02:21.639 --> 00:02:22.520
Xuejiao.

00:02:22.719 --> 00:02:23.719
From now on,

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:25.520
treat me as Gu Zhantian.

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:30.479
To disguise myself as a God of War like Gu Zhantian,

00:02:30.479 --> 00:02:31.360
step one:

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:34.039
my eyes must show a contemptuous

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:34.800
confidence.

00:02:39.319 --> 00:02:40.520
This kid...

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.960
Why did his aura change?

00:02:42.159 --> 00:02:42.960
Step two:

00:02:43.199 --> 00:02:44.639
speak slowly,

00:02:44.639 --> 00:02:45.719
lower my voice,

00:02:45.759 --> 00:02:46.840
and sound pretentious.

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:48.439
Tie Tuo Wang.

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:52.159
Who told you to touch my woman?

00:02:56.439 --> 00:02:57.800
How do you know my name?

00:02:58.039 --> 00:02:59.120
Who exactly are you?

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:02.000
Xuejiao,

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:02.719
let's take a gamble.

00:03:02.719 --> 00:03:03.520
Play along.

00:03:04.599 --> 00:03:05.400
Honey,

00:03:05.560 --> 00:03:06.960
aren't you the God of War?

00:03:07.439 --> 00:03:09.400
Let's teach this young little Tie Tuo Wang

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:09.960
a lesson.

00:03:11.439 --> 00:03:12.240
Shh.

00:03:12.719 --> 00:03:13.039
God...

00:03:13.319 --> 00:03:14.080
God of War?

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:19.599
My Lord.

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:22.120
The Young Master has always been elusive.

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:23.000
Moreover,

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.960
to prevent enemies from knowing his identity,

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:27.120
the Young Master always fights wearing a mask.

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:27.960
Your subordinate

00:03:27.960 --> 00:03:29.120
doesn't know what the Young Master looks like.

00:03:29.319 --> 00:03:30.919
How can I find him?

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:31.800
The Young Master

00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:32.840
is suave and elegant,

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:34.039
surrounded by beauties,

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:35.960
and has a natural aura of dominance.

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:38.199
Once you get there, who the Young Master is

00:03:38.319 --> 00:03:39.759
will be obvious at a glance.

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:40.800
Yes.

00:03:40.840 --> 00:03:42.560
Your subordinate will do his utmost

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:44.719
to help the Young Master unite Haicheng.

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:47.639
Surrounded by beauties,

00:03:48.199 --> 00:03:49.319
with a natural aura...

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:53.319
Why is there no reaction?

00:03:53.919 --> 00:03:55.560
Is the pressure I'm giving not enough?

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:07.319
Tie Tuo Wang

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:09.159
Did you forget what

00:04:09.159 --> 00:04:10.120
you came here for?

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:13.319
Could it be...

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:14.560
He is Young Master Gu?

00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:15.759
Darn.

00:04:15.840 --> 00:04:17.199
I touched his woman.

00:04:17.199 --> 00:04:18.360
Isn't that a death sentence?

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:20.120
Will this work or not?

00:04:20.319 --> 00:04:21.439
If you don't give me a reaction soon,

00:04:21.439 --> 00:04:22.720
I won't be able to hold it together.

00:04:23.439 --> 00:04:24.240
You.

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:25.800
Tell me.

00:04:25.959 --> 00:04:26.759
You...

00:04:27.399 --> 00:04:28.399
Who am I?

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:33.399
Young Master.

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:40.879
When we're outside,

00:04:40.879 --> 00:04:42.040
don't call me Young Master.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:43.639
Call me

00:04:43.639 --> 00:04:44.399
President Lu.

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.560
Don't expose my identity.

00:04:49.759 --> 00:04:50.120
Young...

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:50.959
Ah, no.

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:51.759
President Lu.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:52.600
I'm sorry.

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:53.759
I was wrong.

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:55.199
Please show mercy, President Lu.

00:04:55.399 --> 00:04:56.759
Please show mercy, President Lu.

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.319
That scared me to death.

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:00.560
Good thing I bet right.

00:05:00.920 --> 00:05:02.800
Luckily, this Tie Tuo Wang is just a brute.

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:03.959
Not the sharpest tool in the shed.

00:05:04.839 --> 00:05:06.920
He really is a big dummy.

00:05:07.319 --> 00:05:08.240
Then why don't we

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:09.040
play around a bit more?

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:10.360
Brother,

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:13.519
he squeezed my hand so hard just now.

00:05:14.399 --> 00:05:16.160
Isn't just slapping him

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.000
too light of a punishment?

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.160
Right.

00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:20.120
Too light.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:21.560
I, Tie Tuo Wang, accept my punishment.

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:22.800
Good.

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.199
Then the hand he used to touch me,

00:05:24.199 --> 00:05:25.160
chop it off.

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:32.160
Miss,

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:33.720
now is not the time to play.

00:05:36.959 --> 00:05:37.720
Tie Tuo Wang.

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:41.160
Considering you still have to assist me in the future,

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:42.399
I'll spare you this once.

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:44.680
Today,

00:05:44.680 --> 00:05:45.759
the mistake I made,

00:05:45.759 --> 00:05:46.759
if we were in the Northern Frontier,

00:05:46.959 --> 00:05:47.920
would definitely be a death sentence.

00:05:48.319 --> 00:05:49.720
Losing a hand is already a light punishment.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:50.800
Today,

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:51.759
President Lu has shown mercy.

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:53.120
In the future,

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:54.519
I will definitely pledge my loyalty to the death.

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:55.600
Alright.

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:57.040
Get up.

00:05:57.160 --> 00:05:57.959
Thank you, President Lu.

00:05:58.560 --> 00:05:59.519
Thank you, President Lu.

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:02.800
You guys keep drinking.

00:06:03.920 --> 00:06:04.720
Put it on my tab.

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:05.959
Let's go.

00:06:05.959 --> 00:06:06.759
Wait, President Lu.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.040
Are we

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:12.120
signing the contract?

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:13.399
Are we still discussing it today?

00:06:15.959 --> 00:06:16.759
The contract signing

00:06:20.959 --> 00:06:21.959
will be discussed another day.

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:23.800
Let's go.

00:06:24.360 --> 00:06:25.160
Lu Chengwen.

00:06:25.800 --> 00:06:27.000
Why are you everywhere?

00:06:51.319 --> 00:06:52.360
Who do you think you are?

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:54.000
How dare you speak to President Lu like that?

00:06:56.600 --> 00:06:57.160
Insolent!

00:06:57.399 --> 00:06:58.199
Old Tie,

00:06:58.399 --> 00:06:59.199
watch your mouth.

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:00.879
Why is Tie Tuo Wang

00:07:00.879 --> 00:07:02.560
speaking up for Lu Chengwen?

00:07:02.920 --> 00:07:03.720
Mr. Tie,

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:05.560
I'm the Vice President of Qianfeng Group,

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.639
Gu Zhantian.

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:07.959
And this

00:07:07.959 --> 00:07:09.319
is our President, President Leng.

00:07:09.759 --> 00:07:11.240
We're here to sign a contract.

00:07:11.439 --> 00:07:12.519
You're signing a contract?

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:13.199
Old Tie,

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:14.040
you're talking too much.

00:07:14.639 --> 00:07:15.920
President Gu is my...

00:07:15.920 --> 00:07:16.519
friend.

00:07:16.759 --> 00:07:17.920
Be polite.

00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:19.160
Don't make a fuss.

00:07:19.399 --> 00:07:20.199
Oh.

00:07:20.839 --> 00:07:23.120
How do I talk to him without blowing my cover?

00:07:23.839 --> 00:07:24.720
You know each other?

00:07:26.199 --> 00:07:28.000
Old Tie and I

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:29.240
have known each other for years.

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:30.560
A long time ago, right?

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:32.759
I need to hide the Young Master's identity.

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:33.959
Ah, yes, yes, yes.

00:07:34.040 --> 00:07:35.519
It was many years ago.

00:07:35.800 --> 00:07:36.759
Many years ago?

00:07:38.959 --> 00:07:39.920
Well,

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:40.519
Old Tie,

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:41.639
you and President Gu

00:07:41.639 --> 00:07:43.519
should just talk about that...

00:07:43.519 --> 00:07:44.199
business.

00:07:44.839 --> 00:07:45.800
Listen carefully.

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:47.560
If you don't understand,

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:48.839
just ask a few more times.

00:07:49.360 --> 00:07:49.959
Got it?

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:51.600
All right then.

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:52.519
You guys talk.

00:07:52.639 --> 00:07:53.959
I'll take these two ladies

00:07:53.959 --> 00:07:54.240
over there

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.439
for some drinks.

00:07:56.360 --> 00:07:56.959
Qingqiu,

00:07:56.959 --> 00:07:58.000
don't say too much.

00:07:58.120 --> 00:07:58.959
Come with me.

00:08:00.839 --> 00:08:01.560
President Gu,

00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:02.480
I'll leave things here

00:08:02.480 --> 00:08:03.639
to you for now.

00:08:04.959 --> 00:08:05.759
Let's go.

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:14.360
Stealing hearts and wooing women,

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:16.560
as expected of the Young Master.

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:23.240
So you were just

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:24.560
pretending to be Gu Zhantian?

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:26.519
If it weren't for Brother Chengwen today,

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:27.959
I'd be in real trouble.

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:29.720
When Brother Chengwen said today

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:31.399
that I was his woman,

00:08:31.439 --> 00:08:32.320
he looked so handsome!

00:08:32.799 --> 00:08:33.440
Xu Xuejiao,

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.240
don't interrupt.

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.519
What are you doing here?

00:08:38.120 --> 00:08:39.679
Gu Zhantian used his resources

00:08:39.679 --> 00:08:40.960
to bring five billion in cash.

00:08:40.960 --> 00:08:42.159
He wants to invest in Qianfeng.

00:08:42.519 --> 00:08:43.759
This Qianfeng Group

00:08:43.759 --> 00:08:45.240
might just belong to Gu from now on.

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:46.919
Could that Tie Tuo Wang be

00:08:46.919 --> 00:08:48.600
the one bringing the five billion to sign?

00:08:49.799 --> 00:08:51.159
Well,

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:53.360
it should be him.

00:08:55.039 --> 00:08:57.000
Then why let them negotiate alone?

00:08:57.039 --> 00:08:57.919
If you don't go mess it up,

00:08:57.919 --> 00:08:59.440
what if they actually sign the contract?

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:08.159
Mr. Tie,

00:09:08.759 --> 00:09:10.559
our business plan,

00:09:10.559 --> 00:09:12.440
I've already explained it to you three times.

00:09:12.759 --> 00:09:13.840
Don't tell me

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:15.320
you still don't understand.

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:17.399
Well...

00:09:18.240 --> 00:09:20.200
Tell me about the middle part again.

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:26.799
Why did they send this kind of trash to help me?

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:28.720
Does he think I really don't understand?

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:30.320
The Young Master specifically hinted earlier

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:31.919
to listen a few more times if I don't understand.

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:33.639
Isn't he just asking me to stall for time?

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.200
I'm a seasoned veteran.

00:09:40.159 --> 00:09:41.159
This Tie Tuo Wang...

00:09:41.159 --> 00:09:42.399
It seems he's not that stupid.

00:09:43.039 --> 00:09:43.960
For now,

00:09:43.960 --> 00:09:45.000
we don't need to worry about them signing the contract.

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:45.799
Chengwen,

00:09:46.159 --> 00:09:47.519
although I know saying this

00:09:47.519 --> 00:09:48.559
might be very selfish,

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:50.039
I still hope

00:09:50.039 --> 00:09:51.159
you can help me.

00:09:51.639 --> 00:09:53.519
Make me an enemy of Gu Zhantian?

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:56.000
Brother Chengwen,

00:09:56.000 --> 00:09:56.799
just say it out loud.

00:09:56.799 --> 00:09:58.000
Actually, we can all hear you.

00:09:58.399 --> 00:09:59.919
You want me to help you,

00:10:00.039 --> 00:10:00.559
but...

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:02.519
Forget it.

00:10:02.519 --> 00:10:03.600
I don't know why you've always been

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:04.960
so afraid of Gu Zhantian.

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.559
But if it's really too difficult for you,

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:08.759
I'll figure something out myself.

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:10.120
Sister Qingqiu,

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:11.159
if you really don't want

00:10:11.159 --> 00:10:12.600
to put Brother Chengwen in a tough spot,

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:14.240
you shouldn't keep making that face.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:15.519
Stop talking.

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:17.159
The thing about me is,

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:19.120
my biggest flaw

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:20.000
is being soft-hearted.

00:10:20.200 --> 00:10:21.120
You're not soft-hearted,

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:22.000
you're just a pervert.

00:10:23.399 --> 00:10:24.360
What do you mean a pervert?

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:27.159
Qingqiu,

00:10:27.519 --> 00:10:28.519
I have a plan.

00:10:29.039 --> 00:10:30.360
However,

00:10:30.360 --> 00:10:32.360
I'll need you to cooperate with me later.